videoDetails.Title: War Thunder Air Realistic Guide #1: Defensive Flying
videoDetails.Description:
And I'm back once again! This time, it's Nimbosoup's guide to defensive flying. This will be useful for new and experienced players alike, so hopefully you learn something :) (Shoutout to Halo for the help, as usual!)

Also, thank you guys for all the support! Please leave a like if you enjoyed or learned something, a comment letting me know what that was/what content you'd like to see next, and a sub! 

Also, tune into my stream if you have more questions or wanna hangout with a great community! https://www.twitch.tv/nimbosoup

Check out my discord server if you wanna connect with that community :) https://discord.gg/xSE4XKWyRm
